---
description: Kubernetes rules for app deployment
globs:
  - "/deployment/**"
alwaysApply: false
---

Kubernetes rules:
- Write kubernetes manifests as Helm chart.
- Deploy production app with high availability features.
- Deployment must contain redinessProbe, livenessProbe, resource requests and limits.
- Run pods without root permissions.
- Pull images by digest only.

Helm rules:
- Avoid repeating code, use _helpers.tpl for readability.
- Don't use hard-coded variables. 
